WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Hello ladies of North Brisbane — my name is Coach Hannah.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:18.000
Here at Knight Fitness Lawnton we have a progressive training program for ladies of all ages and all levels.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:24.000
It doesn't matter where you're at in life — we've got you.

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:34.000
We combine weights and conditioning to develop your strength, your fitness, and most importantly your confidence.

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:40.000
All of our classes are coach-led, so you'll have someone guiding you every step of the way.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:50.000
Whatever injury you have, we'll give you alternatives so you can keep progressing toward your goal.

00:00:50.000 --> 00:01:00.000
From the age of 30 we start to lose muscle mass — and that's exactly where strength training comes in.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:12.000
In Women's Club we combine weights and conditioning so you can progress, both in your goals and in life.

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:18.000
Lifting is about far more than appearance — it's about long-term health.

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:28.000
We're not your typical gym. No mirrors, no egos, no pressure or judgement from coaches or peers.

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:38.000
We're a community supporting each other to reach our individual goals.

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:48.000
Whether you're brand new, coming back, or have been lifting for years — our program caters to every level, standard through advanced.

00:01:48.000 --> 00:02:00.000
If you're a lady of North Brisbane and not sure whether to take that step — this is your sign. Reach out and let's have a chat.

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:05.566
Let's help you build confidence and get you where you want to be.
